{
  "stem": "7506.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When it rained, of course, we couldn't play because the earth became a terrible mud, terrible mud.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, and all through the time in the camp, for my outside clothes I had been given by Jopi's father, a pair of ski boots.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Years ago, ski boots were made of leather, not other materials like today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And had thick woolen socks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had an overcoat which was given to me by my aunt in England before I returned to Holland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the overcoat was a hand-me-down from a cousin of mine who was older than me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Didn't fit him anymore, so it was given to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wore that overcoat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I wore that overcoat the whole war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a long, British properly made, woolen material overcoat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I wore that, of course, from the time we were taken away from Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Westerbork about six months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The trains.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Just the trains, the people being called to go on the trains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we left, all the time staying there, because then I realized we were being held there because A, of my mother's place of birth being England, and because I then got to know that when we were taken from Holland to Westerbork, all the diamond people were taken on the same transport, which is known.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was known then and today is known as the diamond transport, diamond transport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's name diamond transport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody that was to do with the diamond business in Amsterdam, and indeed in Holland, all went on that same transport.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all finished up in Westerbork together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All diamond people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "About six months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then of course, it became the winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
